name: Thief Rats in Love - Part 7
description: OMG! That synthetic joint is making me see a duplicate... I'm seeing two rats! What's that up there, hearts? Aff... This naughty rat, in addition to invading my house, still calls a girlfriend. A pot-smoking girlfriend on top! And where did she get that joint? I hope it's not mine. You'll see when I can get up off this rainbow sofa!
